Helpful Tips


Alt + Click expands all children

Instantiate doesn't return as a rigid body so use 'as Rigidbody'

ColourUltilityToHtmlStringRGB(colour here) this can colour text that is shown in the canvas


MeshRenderer[] renderers = = <object instance>.GetComponentsInChildren<MeshRenderers>();
for(int i = 0; i< renderers.length; i++){
	renderers[i].material.color = [a colour you want]
}
to set colour of all mesh renderers